6. REQUIRED FRONTEND FLOWS
==================================================
Support these flows:

FLOW 1: User registration
- user enters name, email, phone, password, city, date of birth
- submits to User Service

FLOW 2: Owner adds a car
- owner enters brand, model, year, city, color, transmission, fuel, seat count, daily rate, document expiry dates
- optionally defines rules

FLOW 3: Renter searches listings
- renter selects city, dates, filters
- frontend calls Listing Service
- renders car cards

FLOW 4: Renter views car details
- show vehicle info
- pricing
- owner rules
- basic availability / eligibility preview

FLOW 5: Renter creates booking
- show booking checkout summary
- include rental price, discount, escrow deposit, total authorization amount
- submit booking to Rental Service

FLOW 6: Owner manages booking requests
- approve or reject booking requests

FLOW 7: Payment summary
- display calculated payment breakdown and escrow amount

FLOW 8: Notifications
- show in-app notifications list
- mark notification as read

FLOW 9: Geo-tracking / pickup
- show current location view placeholder
- show route history placeholder
- show owner dashboard tracking cards

